<p>I have class that has properties:</p>

<pre><code>export class Model {
   public id: number;
   public name: string;
}
</code></pre>

<p>How to make this class observable, to listen changes inm properties.</p>

<p>I need something like that:</p>

<pre><code>let m = new Model();
m.id = 10;
</code></pre>

<p>Listen changes:</p>

<pre><code>m.pipe(map() =&gt; m.id);
</code></pre>
